{"tid":1562473,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"《願榮光歸香港》意大利文版《Che la gloria a Hong Kong》","createTime":"2019-09-12T04:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T05:38:26.000Z","uid":292710,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"576f38ca0e4ad03d6b81aa0630af7ee5f25c5ed3","tid":1562473,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:27:15.000Z","msg":"由於我既意大利文係有限公司，作得唔好請大家唔好笑我。之後係咪要搵人唱？<br />\n<br />\n《Che la gloria a Hong Kong》<br />\n作詞：石室遺錄<br />\n<br />\nQuesta posto volere<br />\nla libert&agrave; di Hong Kong<br />\nlacrima sulla terra per la democrazia<br />\nChe la gloria a Hong Kong<br />\nPerch&eacute; questa paura non &egrave; mai scomparso<br />\nPerch&eacute; lacrime e sangue cadono<br />\nla gente continuer&agrave; a marciare<br />\nSul porto di Victoria<br />\nAbbiamo una nuova rotta<br />\nNella futura terra di libert&agrave; <br />\ne democrazia cambier&agrave; il mondo<br />\nstiamo insieme per la libert&agrave;<br />\nfigli iniziano rivoluzione<br />\nla democrazia e la libert&agrave; <br />\nnon distrugger&agrave; per sempre<br />\nChe la gloria a Hong Kong"},{"pid":"fde39471259ee1494976701ec6facd13d39337c3","tid":1562473,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:27:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2F